# interactive-scroll-animation

This project demonstrates a simple scroll animation using GSAP (GreenSock Animation Platform). It includes a text animation that appears as you scroll down the page.

## Features
- **Page Load Animation**: The content fades in and slides up from the bottom.
- **Scroll Animation**: The content becomes fully visible and animated smoothly as you scroll.

## Getting Started
1. Clone the repository:
    ```bash
    git clone https://github.com/MrRaoelinirina/interactive-scroll-animation.git
    ```
2. Open `index.html` in your browser to view the animation.

